@ADedecker This branch is redefining MulActionHom in the semilinear style.
I went up to a file of yours where you used docs#SMulHom.map_smul.
I have the choice between changing it to `MulActionHom.map_smul underscore sl`, or `_root_.map_smul` (because `Filter` is opened, and there is a confusion). What do you feel is preferable?

